Package com.metsci.glimpse.support.color

Color utility classes for simplifying specification of Glimpse and OpenGL colors.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
GlimpseColor A simple color utility class for converting various color wrapper classes/formats to and from the Glimpse/OpenGl cannonical format (a float[] array with four elements for red, green, blue, and alpha in that order).
